# Local-only throwaway diagnostic/build tools under cmd/. The deployed cmds
# (pringest, prcount, hcount, hingest, backfill-pr-resolved-title) are tracked
# and stay tracked - gitignore only affects untracked files, so one-off probes
# like prcursor/prindex/prusage/prsearch/prtopdiff/prcurrentop/mongo-copy/
# redis-copy are kept locally without polluting commits or the alt flatten.
cmd/
# Stray compiled binary of cmd/hingest at repo root (root-anchored so it does
# not match the tracked cmd/hingest/ source dir).
/hingest
# Stray compiled binary of cmd/tpbingest at repo root (root-anchored so it does
# not match the gitignored cmd/tpbingest/ source dir).
/tpbingest
